beer.beer_description: This classic style pale ale is brewed by Slipstream Brewing Co using Sabro™ hops supplied by Hop Products Australia. Sabro (humulus lupulus neomexicanus) is a sub-species of neomexicanus, a hop indigenous to America’s South West. New and scare on the Australian scene, we are expecting a range of tropical, fruit and citrus aromas amplified by the neomexicanus x-factor that you’ll simply have to try for the experience!
